    "longBusinessSummary": "De Tam Joint Stock Company invests in, develops, and trades in real estate projects in Vietnam. The company develops land funds and urban areas associated with industrial parks; offers real estate services; engages in the real estate consulting and management activities, as well as domestic travel and tourism business; and buys and sells construction materials, electromechanics, refrigeration, sports equipment, and technological products. It is also involved in home business; civil and industrial construction, ground levelling, construction consulting, topographic survey, engineering geology, and hydrogeology activities; buying, sale, and repair of cars; sports activities; operation of entertainment areas, restaurants, and hotels business; airline ticket sales agency business; and construction of technical infrastructure for industrial parks and residential areas. In addition, the company engages in the buying, selling, and rental of construction machinery and equipment, agriculture, forestry, and office products; rents houses, offices, factories, warehouses, as well as for business purposes comprising kiosk and shopping centres; and provision of office and home cleaning and bonsai care, real estate brokerage and auction, real estate advertising and trading floor, and road goods transportation services. De Tam Joint Stock Company was founded in 2003 and is headquartered in Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam.",
